<div class="review-list">
  
  
      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="6717600">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6717600/" class="title-link">日本自卫队是在自慰吗?</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-6717600"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/51161336/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u51161336-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/51161336/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">踏歌而行</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2014-06-26"
      class="main-meta">2014-06-26 15:55:40</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_6717600_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  日本,作为每个中国人心中的最痛,使得我们不由的要关注日本的军力 日本自卫队作为一个神秘的军事力量,一直萦绕在每个爱国者的心间.,因为对日本的厌恶,很多人称之为&#34;日本自慰队&#34; 常言说&#34;知己知彼,百战不殆&#34;,而今天,日本自卫队将揭开它的面纱,让我们可以有机会直接&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">2有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_6717600_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_6717600_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
